         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">2/12/86 ¶ My best thank is due to you, dear Dr Beccari, for the kind sending of the again excellent new fasc. of the Malesia (III,  ¶ ii ¶ ) ¶ , containing a vast mass of new information. Individual  ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">86.12.02</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Odoardo Beccari</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">University of Florence, Science Library: Botany, Archives, Beccari 12/32.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In the archive, this letter is folded within M to O. Beccari, 26 July 1886 (in this edition as 86-07-26c).</p>
               </note>2/12/86</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My best thank is due to you, dear Dr Beccari, for the kind sending of the again excellent new fasc. of the Malesia (III, <seg style="font-variant: small-caps; ">ii</seg>)<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Beccari (1877-90).</p>
               </note>, containing a vast mass of new information. Individual <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Life</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">is too</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">short</hi>
               </seg> f<seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">or science</hi>
               </seg>! My own worldly task will <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">soon</hi>
               </seg> be done, and I shall thus not see the end or much yet of what the young generation, to which <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">you</hi>
               </seg> also belong, will yet achieve for the Goddess Flora. I hope to bring her still (in my bid<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>bit?</p>
               </note> of remaining ear[th]ly<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>editorial addition: MS is damaged.</p>
               </note> career) a wreath of Papuan flowers, particularly from alpine heights!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Kindly tell me, whether you got the nice collection of 650 spec. of dried plants forwarded to you in 1885 through the agency of Tate's Melbourne Carrier-Firm.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to O. Beccari, 15 December 1884.</p>
               </note> A few choice palms were sent by post; — more shall follow; but I must first know, whether the transit through Mr Tate's Agency (with <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">free</hi>
               </seg> delivery) can be relied on.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With regardful remembrance your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Best salutation to the excellent Chevalier D'Albertis.<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Luigi Maria d'Albertis.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
